    Title: Qur’ân
    Location: XLVII 20
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Holy War=Injunction to Holy War
---
And those who believe say： If only a sûrah were revealed! But when a
decisive surah is revealed and war is mentioned therein, thou seest
those in whose hearts is a disease looking at thee with the look of
men fainting unto death. Therefor woe betide them!
